description: Horrison Resources Inc. does not have significant operations. It focuses on exploring various business opportunities in Asia and the United States. The company primarily intends to acquire companies that are wholesalers of agar wood. Previously, it was engaged in the provision of home furniture and closet organizing systems. The company was formerly known as Sichuan Leaders Petrochemical Company and changed its name to Horrison Resources Inc. in April 2018. Horrison Resources Inc. was founded in 2000 and is based in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.
